<h3>Mailing List</h3>

The STFL Mailing list can be subscribed <a
href="http://www.rocklinux.net/mailman/listinfo/stfl">subscribed here</a>.
It is a subscribers-only list, so you need to subscribe first before you
can send mails.

<h3>Implementation Status</h3>
The STFL core and the most important widgets are finished. There are still
some widgets left to be implemented. The error handling isn't perfect yet
(all errors are cought but all errors are fatal and result in program
termination).

